\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {6.4}{\ignorespaces Memory management pipeline (\texttt  {memory\_compressor.py}:598--772, \texttt  {llm.py}:601--650). Parallel chunk summarisation uses asyncio with bounded concurrency (semaphore $= 4$) and falls back to sequential mode if \texttt  {nest\_asyncio} is unavailable. Dual-anchor invariant Inv-1 holds when both anchoring paths succeed; failure modes documented in Chapter~\ref {chap:limits}.}}{24}{figure.caption.21}\protected@file@percent }
